  "About 8%": "",
  "About 50%": "",
  "About 92%": "",
  "For elastic collision: fraction transferred = 4m₁m₂/(m₁+m₂)² = 4(1)(12)/(13)² = 48/169 ≈ 0.284 or about 28%.": "",
  "A hose sprays water (density 1000 kg/m³) at 10 m/s through a nozzle of area 0.002 m². The water hits a wall and comes to rest. What force does the water exert on the wall?": "",
